{"tid":1672901,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想問有冇手足有英文懶人包講成件事嘅來龍去脈","createTime":"2019-10-24T10:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T03:56:39.000Z","uid":276694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3809667414a76ccaeb2ab582d17b69e3d80b8650","tid":1672901,"uid":276694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T10:57:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟宜家就去緊exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次識新朋友仔都會同佢哋講香港嘅事<br />\n但無奈英文真係唔係咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時俾啲朋友仔問返轉頭 真係唔識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想講下香港嘅背景都唔識點講<br />\n所以想問下有冇巴絲可以幫小弟翻譯<br />\n或者有圖俾我airdrop<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說我間U啲NDS多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cd73ec0a8e253704ab8bb844c75315240dbdab","tid":1672901,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:55:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"151aaa7ee635d5f881687456f2352bd7d4372ca7","tid":1672901,"uid":140337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int/1671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int%2F1671&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=3c762100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int/1671</a>"}]}